      "settings": {
        "title": "MADE IN MEXICO WITH LOVE",
        "text": "<b>Maurilio Renteria, State of Jalisco, Mexico</b><Br><br>\n\n<p>Maurilio is an innovator – he learned chaquira techniques from his father at the age of 5 and started his own workshop at the age of 23. He has studied Communication Sciences and performed social services at the state government of Jalisco. He is a father, husband, and artist who is committed to the preservation and well-being of Wixárika artists.</p>",
